romatic scent."}, {"version": "sword", "text": "Comfey picks flowers with its vine and decorates itself with them. For some reason, flowers won\u2019t wither once they\u2019re attached to a Comfey."}, {"version": "ultra-moon", "text": "It picks flowers and sticks them to its body with fluids it produces. The aroma that wafts from its petals has a healing effect."}, {"version": "ultra-sun", "text": "It stretches sticky vines out from its head and picks flowers to adorn itself with. When it doesn\u2019t have any flowers, it feels uneasy."}], "entryGameVersions": ["moon", "shield", "sun", "sword", "ultra-moon", "ultra-sun"], "moveGameGroups": ["scarlet-violet", "sun-moon", "sword-shield", "ultra-sun-ultra-moon"], "evolutionRows": [{"stage": 1, "name": "comfey"}]}